com.paypal.selion.plugins

Class CodeGeneratorMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • com.paypal.selion.plugins.CodeGeneratorMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo

    @Mojo(name="generate",
      defaultPhase=GENERATE_SOURCES)
public class CodeGeneratorMojo
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
    Goal used to generate SeLion Page Object code from PageYAML. Expects {PageObject}Ext.java classes, and PageYAML files to be in src/main/.
